data.meta_description: Shop solid purple brown fabric by the yard, wallpapers and home decor items with hundreds of amazing patterns created by indie makers all over the world. Print and sell your own designs, too!
data.text: All of these great solid purple brown designs are available in fabric by the yard, fabric by the meter, wallpaper and home decor items like curtains, bedding, pillows and dining. Your purchase supports Spoonflower's growing community of artists. Have a design of your own? here to print your custom fabric, wallpaper or home decor!
